            "worstRating": "1"
          },
          "reviewBody": "With my kid studying here for a while now, it’s the fastest growing school in the locality with very good focussed academic and management teams rigorously working  to improve and develop further the school in this locality with as much facilities possible ,like other older and new schools here in this area. They have registered  international and cbse curriculums and the feedback for both streams are good  with attentive well qualified teachers also as other parent's say . Even the facilities are good with new building built with a great design and all kids enjoy it. Also now they brought in private NEET and IIT coaching classes. In summary, keep it up and grow. Few Cons, is more focus to cultural and sports activities ( with a big expanded playground  for both schools ) be given along with academia and fees at slightly higher end for this locality so to be adjusted or maintained inline with other schools in this area.",
          "publisher": {
            "@type": "Organization",
            "name": "Yellow Slate"
          }
        },
